{"type":"answer","id":144285,"parentType":"question","parentId":13864,"uid":28398,"contents":"想深入研究馬克思應該多看一些原教旨的論述<br>\n然後再看一些奧地利學派的著作是怎麼對其批評的 以及從史學理論角度 歷史決定論和對其的批評<br>\n<br>\n我覺得既然感興趣，為什麼不系統的學習政治哲學<br>\n現成的豐富嚴謹的學術成果為什麼不去研究 為什麼非要在意一些快餐理論<br>\n<br>\n尤其關於馬克思的，不妨看看von Mises的兩個小冊子：<br>\n<a href=\"https://mises-media.s3.amazonaws.com/Theory%20and%20History%20An%20Interpretation%20of%20Social%20and%20Economic%20Evolution_1.pdf\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Theory of History</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://www.fee.org/files/doclib/20130703_MarxismUnmasked.pdf\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Marxism Unmasked</a><br>\n以及Hayek的 <a href=\"https://mises.at/static/literatur/Buch/hayek-the-fatal-conceit.pdf\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">the Fatal Conceit</a>","date":"2020-01-31","agreeCount":0,"discussionCount":0}